Dataset Notice
--------------
The METABRIC dataset used in this study is not included in this repository.
It is publicly available under CC BY 4.0 license through:

  cBioPortal : https://www.cbioportal.org
  Kaggle     : https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/raghadalharbi/
               breast-cancer-gene-expression-profiles-metabric

Original data citations:

  Curtis C, et al. Nature. 2012;486:346-352. doi:10.1038/nature10983
  Pereira B, et al. Nature Communications. 2016;7:11479.
  doi:10.1038/ncomms11479

The METABRIC study was funded by Cancer Research UK, the British Columbia
Cancer Agency, and the Wellcome Trust.
